    "timeline": {
      "type": "timeline",
      "blocks": {
        "content-1": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "2021",
            "heading": "Riding Into New Frontiers with Qlife eBike",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Qlife eBike was born from a desire to turn every ride into an adventure. Our first creation, the <strong>Racer Step Over Mountain eBike</strong>, embodies this spirit—pushing limits, exploring the unknown, and delivering innovative technology with uncompromising quality.</p><p>From that first step, we’ve been committed to crafting e-bikes that inspire freedom, joy, and new experiences for riders everywhere. The journey has just begun—and we invite you to explore it with us.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "content-2": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "2022",
            "heading": "Redefining Urban Freedom",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Meet the all-new Qlife <strong>Cityone ST</strong>—a bike designed to make urban riding accessible and stylish for everyone. Its lower frame and seat height offer a sleek look while ensuring easy mounting and comfortable rides for people of all ages, from kids and seniors to those with mobility challenges. The Cityone ST isn’t just transportation—it’s a trusted companion for everyday journeys.</p><p><br/>In 2024, the entire Cityone series received a major upgrade with the launch of Cityone 2.0, bringing enhanced performance, refined design, and even more comfort for urban riders.<br/><br/><br/></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "content-3": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "2023",
            "heading": "<strong>Ignite Your Spirit of Adventure</strong>",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>The Qlife <strong>Racer Fat Tire</strong> and <strong>Racer Plus Fat Tire</strong> eBikes open the door to true off-road freedom—built as rugged companions for bold explorers. Designed for those who crave the thrill of new paths, the Racer series blends powerful performance with advanced suspension, delivering a smooth yet exhilarating ride across mountains, forests, and untamed terrain. Embrace the courage to go farther and redefine what’s possible on your off-road journeys.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "content-4": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "2024",
            "heading": "<strong>Your First Performance Beast</strong>",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Meet the Qlife Spark—an eBike built for riders who crave power, range, and comfort. Reaching speeds over 28 mph and offering up to 65 miles of range, the Spark lets you set your own pace and go further than ever before. More than just an electric bike, it’s the perfect partner for cycling enthusiasts eager to explore new horizons and embrace the thrill of the ride.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
